<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>DT-466E and 530E Diesel Engine Service (1995 through 1999) - SECTION 10: WATER PUMP AND THERMOSTAT - COOLANT
        FILTER - INSTALLATION
    </stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="install" graphiccount="3">
        <title>INSTALLATION</title>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install a new O-Ring and seal into the rear of the coolant filter header (
                <emph type="bold">Figure
                    <hotlnk xrefid="ef1601014">10.14</hotlnk>
                </emph>
                ).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">If removed, place check valves into header and install coolant filter header onto mounting
                pad of front cover and secure with mounting bolts. Tighten to the special torque value (
                <emph type="bold">Figure
                    <hotlnk xrefid="ef1601013">10.13</hotlnk>
                </emph>
                ).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Lubricate coolant filter gasket with clean engine oil and install a new coolant filter.
                Tighten coolant filter until gasket makes contact with the coolant filter header, then tighten one (1)
                additional full turn (
                <emph type="bold">Figure
                    <hotlnk xrefid="ef1601015">10.15</hotlnk>
                </emph>
                ).
            </para>
            <figure id="ef1601013" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="eg5034" filename="../figeg5/eg5034.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 10.13 Remove Coolant Filter Header</caption>
            </figure>
            <figure id="ef1601014" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="eg5377" filename="../figeg5/eg5377.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 10.14 Coolant Filter Header O-Rings</caption>
                <calloutgroup>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">1. Seal</callout1>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">2. Check Valve</callout1>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">3. O-Ring</callout1>
                </calloutgroup>
            </figure>
            <figure id="ef1601015" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="eg5033" filename="../figeg5/eg5033.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 10.15 Installing Coolant Filter</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
